App works great if you know how to adjust the settings to your phone's capabilities. Choppiness isn't an app problem it is called operator error. Your settings are too high for your phone's hardware so the result is dropped frames and trouble rendering everything. Turn down the resolution and/or quality until the choppyness is gone. It should be smooth as silk! Now with that being said, If you have a higher end phone don't hesitate to crank everything up and prepare to be dazzled!
